}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== "P/N: 141711620000J REV: 01A" is silkscreened on the board used to fill this entry. The board is essentially the same as the one used for the [[Belkin F6D6230-4]]. Obviously, the 5GHz radio is unpopulated on this model. RAM on this model ''may vary''. This particular one had a '''EtronTech''' EM68B16CWPA-25H RAM (64MB) chip.
The power adapter included with this model is probably a '''Foxlink''' FA-1501250SUA (100-240VAC ~ 50/60Hz, 0.5A -> 15VDC, 1.25A).
